---
---

<section class="how-i-work" id="how-i-work" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="how-i-work__header reveal">
      <p class="label label-accent">工作方式</p>
      <h2 class="how-i-work__title" id="how-heading">从设计意图到施工落地</h2>
      <p class="how-i-work__sub h-en">How I Work</p>
    </div>

    <ol class="steps" role="list">
      <li class="step reveal">
        <div class="step__number" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
        <div class="step__body">
          <h3 class="step__title">理解设计意图</h3>
          <p class="step__desc">深入阅读方案设计图纸与效果图，与方案设计师充分沟通，准确理解设计目标、风格定位与空间关系，确保后续施工图忠实还原设计初衷。</p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="step__number" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
        <div class="step__body">
          <h3 class="step__title">分析施工可行性</h3>
          <p class="step__desc">结合项目现场条件、地区气候、材料供应与施工工艺，识别方案中可能存在的落地难点，提前制定解决策略，避免施工阶段出现不必要的返工与变更。</p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="step__number" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
        <div class="step__body">
          <h3 class="step__title">转化为施工图</h3>
          <p class="step__desc">将设计意图转化为规范、完整的施工图纸，包含平面定位、竖向设计、铺装大样、构筑物详图、种植图及水电点位图，确保图纸信息清晰、尺寸准确、可直接用于指导施工。</p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="step reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="step__number" aria-hidden="true">04</div>
        <div class="step__body">
          <h3 class="step__title">优化细节与成本</h3>
          <p class="step__desc">在忠于设计效果的前提下，对材料选型、节点构造与施工工序进行合理优化，在保证品质的同时有效控制建造成本，为项目创造实质性价值。</p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="step reveal">
        <div class="step__number" aria-hidden="true">05</div>
        <div class="step__body">
          <h3 class="step__title">支持现场实施</h3>
          <p class="step__desc">施工过程中持续提供图纸答疑与技术支持，根据现场实际情况出具设计变更说明，确保最终建成效果与设计目标高度一致。</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.how-i-work {
  padding-block: var(--space-section);
  background: var(--color-bg-alt);
}

.how-i-work__header {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-3);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
}

.how-i-work__title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-cn);
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.how-i-work__sub {
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--color-ink-faint);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.steps {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  counter-reset: step;
  position: relative;
}

.steps::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 2.25rem;
  top: 1.5rem;
  bottom: 1.5rem;
  width: 1px;
  background: oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.1);
}

.step {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 4.5rem 1fr;
  gap: var(--space-8);
  padding-block: var(--space-10);
  position: relative;
  border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(14% 0.01 60 / 0.07);
}

.step:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.step__number {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-en);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 1.5vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  line-height: 1;
  padding-top: 0.1em;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.step__number::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 2.5rem;
  height: 2.5rem;
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  border-radius: 50%;
  z-index: -1;
  opacity: 0.6;
}

.step__body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-3);
  padding-top: 0.25em;
}

.step__title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-cn);
  font-size: var(--text-md);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

.step__desc {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--color-ink-muted);
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .steps::before { display: none; }
  .step { grid-template-columns: 3rem 1fr; gap: var(--space-4); padding-block: var(--space-8); }
  .step__number { font-size: 1.75rem; }
  .step__number::before { width: 2rem; height: 2rem; }
}
</style>
